%% ====================================================================
%% Sequence 05: Add Stakeholder (owner or assignee, ADR-0005)
%% Task Management System v1.4.4
%%
%% ADR-0005 expands stakeholder management permission to owner ∪ assignee.
%% Stakeholder assignment is visibility-independent (Requirements §3.4.5),
%% so the old "auto-promote to visibility=STAKEHOLDERS" behavior is removed.
%% ====================================================================
sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor Actor as 所有者または担当者
  participant Browser as ブラウザ
  participant Sec as Spring Security
  participant Filter as TenantContextFilter
  participant Ctrl as TaskController
  participant UC as AddStakeholderUseCase
  participant AuthZ as TaskAuthorizationDomainService
  participant UserDir as LegacyUserDirectory<br/>(既存users)
  participant UTRepo as UserTenantRepository
  participant TaskRepo as TaskRepositoryImpl
  participant SHRepo as StakeholderRepositoryImpl
  participant Audit as AuditLogger
  participant DB as MySQL

  Actor->>Browser: タスク詳細 → 「関係者を追加」ボタン
  Browser->>Sec: POST /api/tasks/101/stakeholders<br/>{ "userId": 5 }
  Sec->>Filter: 認証OK (userId=1 または 2, role=MEMBER)
  Filter->>Ctrl: forward (TenantContext set)
  Ctrl->>UC: execute(taskId=101, userId=5, actor)

  UC->>TaskRepo: findById(101, tenantId=11)
  TaskRepo->>DB: SELECT * FROM tasks ...
  TaskRepo-->>UC: task (owner_id=1, assignee_id=2)

  UC->>AuthZ: canManageStakeholders(task, actorUserId)
  Note over AuthZ: 認可ルール: actor が所有者または担当者(ADR-0005)<br/>(基本設計書 §6.2.1「関係者の追加・削除」参照)
  AuthZ->>AuthZ: actorUserId ∈ {task.ownerId, task.assigneeId} ?
  alt 認可失敗 (所有者でも担当者でもない)
    AuthZ-->>UC: throw TaskOwnershipException
    UC->>Audit: log(ADD_STAKEHOLDER_DENIED, actor, taskId=101)
    Audit->>DB: INSERT audit_logs (action='ADD_STAKEHOLDER_DENIED')
    UC-->>Ctrl: TaskOwnershipException
    Ctrl-->>Browser: 403 E_FORBIDDEN<br/>"関係者の追加は所有者または担当者のみ可能です"
    Browser-->>Actor: エラー表示
  else 認可成功 (actor が所有者または担当者)
    AuthZ-->>UC: ✓
  end

  Note over UC,UTRepo: 追加対象ユーザーが同テナント所属か検証
  UC->>UTRepo: findByUserAndTenant(userId=5, tenantId=11)
  UTRepo->>DB: SELECT FROM user_tenants WHERE user_id=5 AND tenant_id=11
  alt 所属していない
    DB-->>UTRepo: 0件
    UTRepo-->>UC: empty
    UC-->>Ctrl: throw NotInTenantException
    Ctrl-->>Browser: 400 E_VALIDATION<br/>"指定ユーザーはテナントに所属していません"
  else 所属
    DB-->>UTRepo: { user_id:5, role:MEMBER, status:ACTIVE }
    UTRepo-->>UC: ✓
  end

  Note over UC: 既存users から表示名を取得 (UI返却用)
  UC->>UserDir: findById(5)
  UserDir->>DB: SELECT id, full_name, email FROM users WHERE id=5<br/>(ReadOnly レプリカ)
  UserDir-->>UC: { id:5, fullName:"佐藤", ... }

  Note over UC,TaskRepo: visibility は変更しない(ADR-0005 §3.4 / 要件定義書 v1.4.3 §3.4.5)<br/>関係者指名は visibility 非依存に可能。参照権限が機能するのは<br/>visibility = STAKEHOLDERS のときのみ(visibility = TENANT のときは<br/>テナント全員が参照可、PRIVATE のときは所有者・担当者のみが参照可)

  UC->>SHRepo: add(TaskStakeholder(taskId=101, userId=5, addedBy=actorUserId))
  SHRepo->>DB: INSERT INTO task_stakeholders<br/>(task_id, user_id, tenant_id, added_by, added_at)
  alt 既に登録済み (重複)
    DB-->>SHRepo: SQLIntegrityConstraintViolation
    SHRepo-->>UC: throw AlreadyStakeholderException
    UC-->>Ctrl: 409 Conflict
  else 新規追加
    DB-->>SHRepo: OK
    SHRepo-->>UC: TaskStakeholder
  end

  UC->>Audit: log(ADD_STAKEHOLDER, actor, taskId=101, addedUserId=5)
  Audit->>DB: INSERT audit_logs

  UC-->>Ctrl: Stakeholder
  Ctrl-->>Browser: 201 + Stakeholder JSON
  Browser-->>Actor: 関係者リストに追加表示

  Note over UC,Audit: 関係者追加・削除は所有者または担当者が実施可能(ADR-0005、NIST AC-3)<br/>関係者追加通知は MVP では実装しない(ADR-0005 §3.4、Phase 2 で整理)
